<header>
	<h1>Latte Art: Tracked. Improved.</h1>
	<p>
		Tired of scattered photos and guesswork in your latte art practice?
		LatteArtist is a simple iOS journal designed to help you intentionally
		log pours, track techniques, and clearly visualize your improvement over
		time. Developed with feedback from the home barista community on Reddit.
	</p>
</header>

<style>
	/* Styles specific to Header component */
	header {
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 3);
		text-align: center;
	}

	h1 {
		/* Global color handled in Layout */
		font-optical-sizing: auto;
		font-size: 2.8em;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 0.5);
		line-height: 1.2;
		max-width: 700px; /* Constrain width like paragraph */
		margin-left: auto; /* Center constrained h1 */
		margin-right: auto; /* Center constrained h1 */
	}

	header p {
		font-size: 1.1em;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		max-width: 700px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	/* Responsive adjustments for h1 are in Layout's global styles */
</style>
